1: Create subnet group for memcache that contains  the Saas private subnets

2: We can use the default parameter group

2: Select Domain name  -- Decide some naming convention
   Engine Version Compatibility:1.4.34

3: Select node type and number of nodes acording to the requirement
   select the subnet group created in step 1
   Select the security group

4: Select maintainance window on a weekday 4 to 4:30 and create memcache


5: Test connection to memcache by using the below command

telnet ost-stag2-sand-mem.xsap5a.0001.use1.cache.amazonaws.com 11211
